    <keyword>OPTION_PD_EXCLUDE</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines an optional mechanism to allow exclusion of one specific prefix from a delegated prefix set when using DHCPv6-based prefix delegation.  The new mechanism updates RFC 3633. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
